{
  "stem": "393.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Auschwitz was a cooler place, according to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Auschwitz was clean-- kept clean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we never had a lice on us or anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had water to drink and to wash ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were able to wash ourselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't have soap.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But anyway-- but Bergen-Belsen, there hardly was food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it was the end already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took too many people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was no place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were in a-- we were put in a corridor-- sat on the floor, again, like with a-- with our knees to our chest.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But there were-- it was packed!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The toilet was overrun.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was no water to wash or to drink anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We got a tea in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We got some kind of a food which didn't have any taste-- a little, just sometimes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We didn't get-- it was disorganized already, absolutely!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then, then the tragedy came that the typhus-- typhus-- typhoid-- typhus breakout.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Lice-- first of all, it's sad to tell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Lice is something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I think if I would see a lice now, I will die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Lice was the most, most, most terrible thing in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You couldn't do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You will absolutely have it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "First, when we got-- we're very clean when we got there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then mixing with them, sleeping with them on the floor, whatever, of course, we got it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then, we tried to clean ourselves a little bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But-- but it came to a point where there's-- where nothing helps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing helped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We took off our dresses, and we-- we-- went-- the floor was our place, anyway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to sleep without anything, because then-- then-- then we could just sweep off the lice, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have-- it didn't bother us so much.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
